title: CS Universitatea Alexandria
text:
Clubul Sportiv Universitatea Alexandria, commonly known as Universitatea Alexandria, or simply U Alexandria, is a Romanian women's <a href="Association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="Alexandria%2C%20Romania">Alexandria</a>, <a href="Teleorman%20County">Teleorman County</a>, <a href="Romania">Romania</a>. The team was founded in 2012, since then playing constantly in the Romanian leagues.
Universitatea Alexandria currently plays in the Liga I, first tier of the Romanian women's football system, after ranking 4th at the end of the 2017–18 season.
